LORD ELDER responded, "I am sure that thier shuttle has the sensors they need."

Meanwhile the shuttle that WINDLORD and PERCEPTOR were flying in
showed the humans as retreating further into their little forest area,
up ahead they could detect a small village were other PROTOHUMANS
could be scanned as well.

From the readouts thoes in the viallge were the women and children
that these men were coming back to.

At the same time overhead the shuttle that NIGHTSHIFT, POLAR CLAW and
the rest were on also flew in.

"Windlord." came POLAR CLAW's  voice over the comlink. "We are ready
to transfer Nightshift to your ship."

POLARCLAWS's ship came in to hover right next to WINDLORD'S shuttle.
If WINDLORD allowed it the two ships could link up temporailly.
